text: Ralfs Grīnbergs (born November 10, 1995) is a Latvian ice hockey player currently playing for the HK Rīga of the MHL. ==Playing career== Grīnbergs began his hockey career playing in minor and junior Latvian hockey leagues. In 2013/2014 season he joined HK Rīga Dinamo Rīga minor league affiliate. He made his KHL debut on October 15 in defeat against Jokerit. ===International=== Grīnbergs participated at the 2014 World Junior Ice Hockey Championships as a member of the Latvia men's national junior ice hockey team. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian ice hockey defencemen Category:HK Riga players Category:Dinamo Riga players Category:Mississippi RiverKings (SPHL) players
